## Suggested Commands

```bash
# Create branch
git checkout -b fix/cloudflare-governance-automation-index

# Verify which scripts exist before writing index
for script in \
  "infra/cloudflare/scripts/validate-cloudflare-config.sh" \
  "infra/cloudflare/scripts/check-secret-leaks.sh" \
  "infra/cloudflare/scripts/scan-tunnel-configs.sh" \
  "infra/cloudflare/scripts/scan-dns-ownership.sh" \
  "infra/cloudflare/scripts/scan-workers-routes.sh" \
  "infra/cloudflare/scripts/scan-workers-edge-bindings.sh" \
  "infra/cloudflare/scripts/scan-terraform-cloudflare-ownership.sh" \
  "infra/cloudflare/scripts/score-cloudflare-change-risk.sh" \
  "infra/cloudflare/scripts/scan-cloudflare-environment-boundaries.sh"; do
  [ -f "$script" ] && echo "EXISTS: $script" || echo "MISSING (GAP): $script"
done

# Verify which workflows exist
for wf in \
  ".github/workflows/cloudflare-release-readiness.yml" \
  ".github/workflows/deploy-worker.yml" \
  ".github/workflows/validate.yml" \
  ".github/workflows/ci.yml"; do
  [ -f "$wf" ] && echo "EXISTS: $wf" || echo "MISSING (GAP): $wf"
done

# After writing files
cat docs/infra/cloudflare-governance-automation-index.md
cat docs/infra/cloudflare-scanner-index.md
cat docs/infra/cloudflare-workflow-index.md
cat docs/infra/cloudflare-evidence-output-index.md

# Verify all 9 scripts mentioned
grep -c "scan-\|validate-\|score-\|check-" docs/infra/cloudflare-scanner-index.md

# Secret check
grep -RInE '(token|secret|password|credential|api[_-]?key)' \
  docs/infra/cloudflare-governance-automation-index.md \
  docs/infra/cloudflare-scanner-index.md \
  docs/infra/cloudflare-workflow-index.md \
  docs/infra/cloudflare-evidence-output-index.md || echo "No secrets found"

# Commit
git add docs/infra/cloudflare-governance-automation-index.md \
        docs/infra/cloudflare-scanner-index.md \
        docs/infra/cloudflare-workflow-index.md \
        docs/infra/cloudflare-evidence-output-index.md \
        infra/cloudflare/README.md
git commit -m "docs(cloudflare): index governance automation"

git push origin fix/cloudflare-governance-automation-index
gh pr create --title "docs(cloudflare): index governance automation" \
  --body "Phase 22: Adds master governance automation index, scanner index (9 scripts + GAPs), workflow index, evidence output index. Read-only. No deploy. No secrets."
```

---

## Final Response Format for AI Agent

When this phase is complete, report:

1. Files created (list with paths)
2. Files updated (list with paths)
3. Scanner index summary: N found, N GAPs
4. Workflow index summary: N found, N GAPs
5. Evidence output index summary: N entries
6. Validation commands run and their output summary
7. Any warnings (missing entries, unlabeled GAPs)
8. Git status summary (`git diff --stat`)
9. Suggested commit command (already done or ready to run)

**Do not claim that anything was deployed.**
**Do not claim that Cloudflare was changed.**
**Do not claim that Terraform was applied.**
**GAP items must be clearly labeled as missing — do not create stub scripts in this phase.**
